body:
# Flora Formae

**Are you tired of making beautiful flower arrangements just to look at them from above a see an empty grass field?**

**Do you wish those boring cross shapes could be replaced with something with a bit more jazz?**

**Are you like me, and get bothered by minor things in a silly block game?**

**Do you often find yourself alone in the middle of the night thinking about the meaning of existence?**


### Well, look no further! Three of your problems can be solved right here!
##

Flora Formae adds custom models to give certain nature related blocks their own identity, while trying to stay as close as possible to the Minecraft visual style. No mods are required, though it does optionally support [Respackopts](https://modrinth.com/mod/respackopts) (resourcepack 1.4+ for Minecraft 1.21+).

